title: Umbrella Academy Viktor Vinyl Figure
body_html:
"I'm gonna make this right" Viktor makes his debut to Youtooz to help us avert the apocalypse! Just don't ask who triggered it ok?! Standing at 5.2 inches tall with a blank expression on his face and pursed lips, he holds an open tattered black umbrella over his head as their short black hair is swept to the side with its fringe resting over their forehead. With one hand in his pocket, they wear a fitted black jacket over a dark grey jumper with its hood folded over the collar and a white t-shirt along with simple blue jeans over black boots. The exterior of his packaging sees Victor turned away as silhouetted birds fly across its cream-colored background. The interior of his packaging is a stark black covered in red and white flying bullets, knives, umbrellas and crosshairs which continues onto the protective sleeve where his figure can be seen through the large clear window at the packaging's front.

  • Height 5.2"
  • This collectible ships in a matte, embossed, protective outer sleeve and a custom sized plastic protector for maximum protection during shipping
